01:11.521 --> 01:13.465
Big Clippers fan.

01:13.590 --> 01:15.133
Things can change
for the better, Roger.

01:15.258 --> 01:16.326
And I'm going to prove it.

01:16.492 --> 01:18.253
This little guy will be a butterfly.

01:18.378 --> 01:19.746
You'll see.

01:19.912 --> 01:22.290
