01:35.678 --> 01:37.372
Oh, man, here it comes.

01:37.497 --> 01:39.307
It's gonna be...
Wait, what's this?

01:39.473 --> 01:41.143
It's a costume!

01:41.268 --> 01:42.878
And it's lovely!

01:43.003 --> 01:45.447
Leather vest, non-matching
leather pants,

01:45.572 --> 01:47.816
Albuquerque Zoo
Discovery Center T-shirt...

01:47.941 --> 01:49.568
Why did I ever stop wearing this?

01:49.859 --> 01:51.136
Well, what character is it for?

01:51.402 --> 01:52.571
I can't remember.

01:52.737 --> 01:54.055
Well, who cares?!

01:54.180 --> 01:55.891
I'm taking this show into town.

01:56.016 --> 01:58.510
This is the perfect outfit
for getting yogurt!

01:58.635 --> 02:00.918
I'm gonna get so many tiny M&Ms!

02:01.043 --> 02:02.397
Get out of there, Snickers fragment,

02:02.522 --> 02:04.041
you're not welcome here!

02:05.325 --> 02:06.451
I got it!

02:06.576 --> 02:07.435
You opened it last time!

02:07.560 --> 02:08.436
Cup check!

02:08.561 --> 02:10.672
Punk.

02:10.838 --> 02:13.742
Ooh, Mr. and Mrs.
Stan and Francine Smith?

02:13.867 --> 02:14.709
Mm-hmm.
Aah!

02:14.834 --> 02:15.802
Can we help you?

02:15.968 --> 02:18.597
It's me... Tungee!

02:18.763 --> 02:19.447
Who?

02:19.572 --> 02:21.816
Tungee from Nigeria!

02:21.941 --> 02:23.652
I was the child you sponsored for

02:23.777 --> 02:26.271
just the price of
a cup of coffee a day!

02:26.396 --> 02:28.139
Oh, my god! Tungee?

02:28.264 --> 02:29.975
You're real?

02:30.100 --> 02:31.643
What are you doing here?

02:31.768 --> 02:33.945
I come to live with you!

02:34.070 --> 02:36.740
Wait, does this mean Africa is real?

02:36.906 --> 02:39.508
